" play operator

nnoremap <buffer> <localleader>p :set operatorfunc=alda#playing#PlayOperator<cr>g@
nmap <buffer> <localleader>pp V<localleader>p
vnoremap <buffer> <localleader>p :<c-u>call alda#playing#PlayOperator(visualmode())<cr>

